{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\udde9 <i>2024: Mosaic Retrospective</i> is <strong>digital cross-stitch</strong>. A meditative game about completing a single <strong>enormous</strong>\u00a060,000 piece grid puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f In this entry<i>\u00a0</i>in the <i>Mega Mosaic</i> series, you'll slowly reveal a pixel art collage of major news events from the last year, ranging from politics to sport, climate change to pop culture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udca3 If you\u2019re familiar with minesweeper, you\u2019re ready to dive in! Use the numbered clues (0-9) to uncover light tiles that gradually reveal an intricate, detailed mosaic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfb6 Whether you're engrossed in your favourite podcasts or listening to your favourite tunes, 2024: Mosaic Retrospective serves as the perfect backdrop to enhance your experience. Or choose from the soothing built-in  soundtrack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u23f3 Dozens of Hours of Addictive Gameplay!\u00a0<i>2024: Mosaic Retrospective</i> offers hours of meditative, yet challenging gameplay as you piece together the events that shaped the year.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3380760/extras/UNICEF_Logo.png?t=1735657605\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>If you like this free game, please consider supporting the UNICEF fundraiser that the game is supporting! You can find the link to the fundraiser in the settings menu within the game.</strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Spacewalk","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3380760/f6c9cd7a751c9fded9ea3b0b0640683afb169c9d.jpg"},{"name":"Remote Control","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3380760/261fa7236703493daa5519cb8ce6a80ac9631ca4.jpg"},{"name":"Far Side","path